To enable support in FlightGear you must manually copy some of the files
from this directory tree to proper FlightGear directories. See ltr_pipe's
README file for usage information.

* Files description
====================

Stand-alone protocol file:

  fgfs/Protocol/linuxtrack.xml


Protocol file for linuxtrack.nas script:

  fgfs/Protocol/linuxtrack.nas.xml


Nasal script for linuxtrack.nas.xml protocol file:

  fgfs/Nasal/LinuxTrack/linuxtrack.nas


Example joystick file:

  fgfs/Input/Joysticks/LinuxTrack/uinput-abs.xml

